===Etymology===
From a variant of the {{etyl|enm|en}} noun {{m|enm|even}} (itself from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{m|ang|ǣfen}}), with a pre-1200 loss of the terminal '-n', which was mistaken for an inflection. <ref>http://dictionary.reference.com/browse/eve</ref> See also the now archaic or poetic {{m|en|even||evening}}, from the same source.

